# Context filter for the BACKEND image (repo-root context, root Dockerfile).
# The frontend image uses frontend/Dockerfile.dockerignore instead (BuildKit prefers the
# Dockerfile-adjacent ignore file), so entries here only shape the backend build context.
.git
**/bin
**/obj
**/.idea
**/.vs
frontend/node_modules
frontend/dist
frontend/.next
frontend/design-reference
frontend/coverage
load/results
docs
**/*.md
**/*.tsbuildinfo
